purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains terms related to administration of etesevimab.),(Data Element Scope: ),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes introduction of etesevimab into central or peripheral veins via open or percutaneous routes.),(Exclusion Criteria: Excludes administration of other monoclonal antibodies (e.g., abciximab, infliximab) and routes of administration that do not involve open or percutaneous procedures (i.e. oral administration).)
